<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#6d02225af0e7c46d2d17859f468ff844>.
<#6d02225af0e7c46d2d17859f468ff844> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/b451cab6-2a8f-4b14-a125-fe0c49a6c9aa>;
