<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/c6ae10b6-6a18-4e15-9444-fbd746f4609d> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__83427.
_:b0__83427 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
