}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#51b06949f5c1e41a81a678061abbb113>.
<#51b06949f5c1e41a81a678061abbb113> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2462f23e-b3b9-4f2c-ad37-ba52472cc6ca>;
