<#1e0a4d18e618f9ff23e7ca69c5bbdecd> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N79223>;
