<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d6241f76df89f129ab9246f8beb7f87a>.
<#d6241f76df89f129ab9246f8beb7f87a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://ckan-malmo.dataplatform.se/dataset/4bc0a377-29f3-4bf6-94f2-a1ff243413a2>;
