    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021002932>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Data för historiska atmosfäriska avsättningar av sulfat, nitrat och ammonium från land och frakt i Östersjön.\n\nNär du använder det här datasetet kan du också citera: Omstedt, A., Edman, M., Claremar, B., and Rutgersson, A.: Modelling the contributions to marine acidification from deposited SOx , NOx , and NHx in The Baltic Sea: past and present situations, Cont. Shelf Res., 111, 234���249, https://doi.org/10.1016/j.csr.2015.08.024, 2015."@sv, "Historical atmospheric depositions of sulphate, nitrate, and ammonium from land and shipping in the BalticSea.\n\nWhen using this dataset, please also cite: Omstedt, A., Edman, M., Claremar, B., and Rutgersson, A.: Modelling the contributions to marine acidification from deposited SOx , NOx , and NHx in The Baltic Sea: past and present situations, Cont. Shelf Res., 111, 234–249, https://doi.org/10.1016/j.csr.2015.08.024, 2015."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5879/ecds/2017-10-10.2/1#distribution>;
